OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784121522
OL,3,CLast person sentenced over 2024
OL,4,Cmigrant hotel riot
OL,6,FA 120th person has become the last to
OL,7,Fbe jailed over rioting outside a hotel
OL,8,Fhousing migrants in 2024.
OL,10,FAshley Ivermee, 25, of South Drive,
OL,11,FBarnsley, was given an 18-month
OL,12,Fsentence after pleading guilty to
OL,13,Fviolent disorder following the
OL,14,Fincident at the Holiday Inn Express
OL,15,FHotel in Rotherham.
OL,17,FHis sentence takes the total amount of
OL,18,Fprison time handed out to those
OL,19,Finvolved to more than 300 years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
