OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784121522
OL,3,CLast person sentenced over 2024
OL,4,Cmigrant hotel riot
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police's head of
OL,7,Fcrime, Ch Supt Laura Koscikiewicz
OL,8,Fpraised the public's help in
OL,9,Fconvicting those responsible.
OL,11,F"In the weeks and months after this
OL,12,Fdisgusting display of thuggery, our
OL,13,Flocal communities stood up and said
OL,14,Fthis wasn't acceptable," she said.
OL,16,F"The public response to what was a
OL,17,Fdark day for South Yorkshire was
OL,18,Fnothing short of outstanding."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
