OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784121522
OL,3,CLast person sentenced over 2024
OL,4,Cmigrant hotel riot
OL,6,FHundreds of people gathered at the
OL,7,Fhotel on 4 August 2024 as trouble
OL,8,Fbroke out across the country in the
OL,9,Fwake of the murders of three girls in
OL,10,FSouthport.
OL,12,FObjects were thrown at police who were
OL,13,Ftrying to protect the hotel, where
OL,14,Fmore than 200 asylum seekers and 22
OL,15,Fstaff were trapped inside.
OL,17,FSome of the hotel's windows were
OL,18,Fsmashed in what South Yorkshire Police
OL,19,Fcalled a "disgusting display of
OL,20,Fthuggery".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
