PN,33204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784121522
OL,3,CLast person sentenced over 2024
OL,4,Cmigrant hotel riot
OL,6,FA group of rioters got into the hotel
OL,7,Fand a bin was pushed against the wall
OL,8,Fand set alight.
OL,10,FA total of 64 officers were injured in
OL,11,Fthe violence along with police horses
OL,12,Fand a dog, South Yorkshire Police said.
OL,14,FThe incident caused millions of pounds
OL,15,Fworth of damage.
OL,17,FThe following investigation was one of
OL,18,Fthe biggest in the history of South
OL,19,FYorkshire Police, involving analysis
OL,20,Fof about 100,000 hours of footage.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
